OL,2,MTree Grafting in the Personality
OL,4,MDisorder Wing
OL,6,CJoe Robinson
OL,7,CFri 13:50-14:20
OL,8,CStage B
OL,10,GWhat happens when you put a
OL,11,Gtherapeutic tree nursery inside a
OL,12,Ghigh-security prison? This talk covers
OL,13,Gthe practicalities and surprises of
OL,14,Gsetting up and running horticultural
OL,15,Gprogrammes in custodial settings, from
OL,16,Gnegotiating with security to working
OL,17,Galongside people with complex and
OL,18,Goften severe mental health conditions.
OL,19,GWe'll look at why plants and growing
OL,20,Gthings seem to reach people that other
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
